\c 4
\s Mufaro nerugre zviri kuna Jehovha
\d kumutungamiriri wenziyo; nemitengeramwa.Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p 1ndipindurei kana ndichidana,Mwari wokururama kwangu;Pakumanikidzwa kwangu makandiisa pakafarikana;ndinzwirei tsitsi, munzwe munyengetero wangu.2 Nhai vanakomana vavanhu kukudzwa kwangu kuchashandurwa kunyadziswa kusvikira rinhiko? Muchda zvisina maturo , nekutsvaka nhema kusvikira rinhi? 3 Asi zivai kuti Jehovha akazvitsaurira munhu ,anomuda Jehovha uchanzwa kana ndichidana kwaari. 4 Ityai murege
